Class PathValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.psu.cse.siis.coal.values.PathValue
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NullPathValue

    public class PathValue
extends Object
    A COAL value for a single execution path. This is essentially a collection of field values.
